Use this README file to introduce your application and point to useful places in the API for learning more.
Run "rake doc:app" to generate API documentation for your models, controllers, helpers, and libraries.


- Billspike is intended to help house shares manage the common bills and distribute what's owed to everyone
- each user should have a weight in the share
- a user can be a general manager, an owner of a share, or an invitee taking part in a share
- a new user can create a share, not search
- an owner can invite others by email
- a user can add items bought
- an owner can set up reminders to be sent to users to pay their dues